data.description: This "like new" ranch home in desirable Flowers Plantation offers a remarkable and low-maintenance living space in a vibrant community. The home features a modern, open concept design that seamlessly connects living spaces, promoting a sense of togetherness and social interaction. Notable design elements include 10ft tray ceilings in the foyer, living room and owner's retreat. The kitchen has a 13ft long pantry, stainless steel appliances, gas cooktop, beautiful white quartz countertops and island. The private owner's retreat includes a tiled, zero-entry, L-shaped shower and double vanity sink. A versatile sunroom located at the front of the home can be used as an office, or a den, offering flexibility in it's use. The property boasts a wooded backyard view with a maintenance-free lawn and an irrigation system, making outdoor enjoyment hassle-free. Convenient location, with shopping, dining, medical facilities, dental services and recreational opportunities at the nearby East Triangle YMCA, accessible via a short golf cart drive.
